Package garuntimeenv.interfaces

Interface Property

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CrossoverOperators, IFitnessFunction<T>, IMutation, IProblemRepresentation, Selection
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InsertionMutation, InversionMutation, JobShopPreferenceListRep, ListProperty, LOX, MakespanFitnessFunction, NumberProperty, OX, PMX, RouletteWheelSelection, SortedSelection, SwapMutation
    public interface Property
    Each element that is a property instance shall implement this interface. In this regard belong genetic operators, selection algos, and the hyper parameter values which are wrapped through the NumberProperty wrapper which extends the Property interface.
